A great battle has been initiated.

16
00:01:47,452 --> 00:01:49,647
The mother of all battles.

17
00:01:49,732 --> 00:01:51,006
(Bush) Our objectives...

18
00:01:51,092 --> 00:01:53,367
..in the Persian Gulf area clear,...

19
