..and without condition.

23
00:02:07,252 --> 00:02:09,527
(Bush) The liberation of Kuwait...

24
00:02:09,612 --> 00:02:11,409
..has now entered a fllnal phase.

25
00:02:11,492 --> 00:02:15,280
l have therefore directed
to use all forces available,...

26
00:02:15,372 --> 00:02:17,203
..including ground forces,...

27
00:02:17,292 --> 00:02:20,170
..to eject the Iraqi army from Kuwait.

28
00:02:21,532 --> 00:02:23,329
(Peter Arnett)
At this point it seems inevitable...

29
00:02:23,412 --> 00:02:25,880
..that the ground war is only hours away.

30
00:02:25,972 --> 00:02:28,281
Peter Arnett, Baghdad.

31
00:02:37,652 --> 00:02:41,201
Don't ever for one minute
underestimate the enemy,...

32
00:02:41,292 --> 00:02:43,169
..but remember, we're better soldiers.

33
00:02:43,252 --> 00:02:47,689
We're fighting with better equipment,
we're better trained and a lot smarter.

34
00:02:47,772 --> 00:02:51,321
Sleep deprivation.
Our soldiers been up 46, 48 hours,...

35
00:02:51,412 --> 00:02:53,801
..so stay on top of 'em.
Maintain your intervals.

36
00:02:53,892 --> 00:02:54,768
Any questions?

37
00:02:56,212 --> 00:02:58,009
Let's have a Little prayer.

38
00:02:58,092 --> 00:03:00,162
Dear God, protect us...

39
00:03:00,252 --> 00:03:03,289
..as we protect our country
we so dearly Love.

40
