445
00:26:25,452 --> 00:26:27,443
Oh, my God!

446
00:26:30,052 --> 00:26:31,007
Oh!

447
00:26:32,412 --> 00:26:33,640
Whoa! Shit!

448
00:26:33,732 --> 00:26:35,723
Whoa! Oh, God!

449
00:26:35,812 --> 00:26:37,928
Hang on, llario! Grab a hold of me!

450
00:26:38,012 --> 00:26:39,411
Don't let go of me! Pull me in!

451
00:26:39,492 --> 00:26:42,609
Hang on.
Come on, llario! Pull yourself up!

452
