478
00:28:02,612 --> 00:28:03,840
Hu-ah.

479
00:28:03,932 --> 00:28:05,570
Hu-ah.

480
00:28:05,652 --> 00:28:08,325
Once upon a time,
I was humping in the delta.

481
00:28:08,412 --> 00:28:10,368
- With who?
- The 9 th.

482
00:28:10,452 --> 00:28:13,091
- You kicked some serious butt.
- That's right.

483
00:28:13,172 --> 00:28:15,732
- One for my friend...
- Colonel Nat Serling.

484
00:28:15,812 --> 00:28:19,600
Make it a double for Colonel Serling.
Tony Gartner, Washington Post.

485
00:28:21,532 --> 00:28:25,161
They won't find any criminal culpability
in the AI Bathra incident.

486
00:28:25,252 --> 00:28:26,765
You got nothing to worry about.

487
00:28:26,852 --> 00:28:28,251
