501
00:29:24,052 --> 00:29:25,883
..on the two downed choppers.

502
00:29:29,652 --> 00:29:31,608
(screaming)

503
00:29:34,492 --> 00:29:35,481
Oh!

504
00:30:18,972 --> 00:30:19,882
Sir!

505
00:30:23,172 --> 00:30:26,005
All right, this is antifungal cream,...

506
00:30:26,092 --> 00:30:29,971
..but to kill the athlete's foot when
