538
00:31:43,572 --> 00:31:45,449
(laughs)

539
00:31:48,852 --> 00:31:49,841
So...

540
00:31:49,932 --> 00:31:52,241
..tell me what happened at AI Kufan.

541
00:32:02,652 --> 00:32:04,563
See, I'd, uh...

542
00:32:05,892 --> 00:32:08,565
