00:34:55,812 --> 00:34:57,450
As soon as it gets dark, we dig in.

596
00:34:57,532 --> 00:34:58,601
Then we wait.

597
00:34:58,692 --> 00:34:59,681
For what?

598
00:34:59,772 --> 00:35:01,251
For the good guys.

599
00:35:01,772 --> 00:35:04,081
(laughing and shouting in Arabic)

600
00:35:05,052 --> 00:35:08,283
You won't think it's so funny
when I nail your fucking ass!

601
00:35:11,492 --> 00:35:13,448
Yeah, they were laughing.

602
00:35:15,212 --> 00:35:17,567
You about, uh... You done?

603
00:35:17,772 --> 00:35:20,445
So tell me what happened...

604
00:35:20,532 --> 00:35:22,602
..during the night.

605
00:35:22,732 --> 00:35:24,962
You were there. You saw the nights.

606
00:35:25,052 --> 00:35:26,644
You know, just... it was black.

607
00:35:26,732 --> 00:35:27,881
Just... black.

608
00:35:27,972 --> 00:35:29,928
Tell me what happened that night.

609
00:35:31,492 --> 00:35:33,608
Well, she put us on two-hour watches.

610
00:35:33,692 --> 00:35:39,449
Um... it's not like
any of us were going to sleep anyway.

611
00:35:41,932 --> 00:35:44,685
