1457
01:20:19,275 --> 01:20:21,391
Guys under your command.

1458
01:20:22,475 --> 01:20:24,272
How'd it feel?

1459
01:20:24,355 --> 01:20:25,674
Bad, right?

1460
01:20:25,755 --> 01:20:27,188
Very bad, son.

1461
01:20:27,275 --> 01:20:28,230
Very bad.

1462
01:20:28,315 --> 01:20:29,987
(train whistle)

1463
01:20:31,155 --> 01:20:33,225
And you didn't even mean to kill them.

1464
01:20:36,035 --> 01:20:37,912
I've been a good soldier.

1465
01:20:38,995 --> 01:20:41,463
A good soldier.

1466
01:20:41,675 --> 01:20:43,506
