1470
01:20:53,475 --> 01:20:56,387
Johnny ''Night Train'' Monfriez.

1471
01:20:59,595 --> 01:21:00,948
Now get out.

1472
01:21:01,235 --> 01:21:02,987
You don't want to do this, son.

1473
01:21:03,075 --> 01:21:04,110
Let me help you.

1474
01:21:04,195 --> 01:21:07,153
- It's too late.
- It's never too late. Look at me.

1475
01:21:07,235 --> 01:21:10,466
Things get fucked up in war.
I don't care what happened to you.

1476
01:21:10,555 --> 01:21:11,544
You can't do this.

1477
01:21:11,635 --> 01:21:12,590
Wrong!

1478
01:21:14,155 --> 01:21:16,225
I can't do anything else.

1479
01:21:16,315 --> 01:21:20,194
Yes, you can. You can put the car in reverse.
Put the gun down.

1480
01:21:20,275 --> 01:21:21,503
We can help each other.

1481
01:21:23,595 --> 01:21:26,428
I don't want to lose another good soldier.

1482
01:21:29,355 --> 01:21:30,344
